Description: Patched DuckDB extensions for ColdFront tiered storage
 The patched DuckDB extensions ColdFront's cold tier needs — iceberg, avro,
 azure, and postgres_scanner — carrying ColdFront's bakery-aware-commit-refresh
 and interop patches. They are loaded by pg_duckdb; point
 duckdb.extension_directory at the install dir (see the installed config sample)
 so pg_duckdb loads these instead of downloading the unpatched upstream builds.
